When a file is visited, function `set-auto-mode' (see [[Manual:set-auto-mode]]) is called to determine the right MajorMode to use.

It looks for a ##mode:## string, then applies these variables in turn:
* [[auto-mode-interpreter-regexp]]
* [[magic-mode-alist]]
* [[auto-mode-alist]]
* [[magic-fallback-mode-alist]] (new in Emacs 22)

----
